dct_description_sm: Shows built up areas, roads, railway, important places and buildings. "List of names and other miscellaneous informations are printed on reverse." On verso: Sketch map of Faisalābād Includes place name index, train, bus and air routes and service, and miscellaneous and tourist information on verso. "Government of Pākistān copyright reserved." Area surveyed 1995-96. "REG. No. 187 RWD '97 ..."
